"Sharing Boating Bliss, Where Kinships Set Sail"​ 
 
1st in the World Sunreef Supreme 68S Luxury Catamaran, EagleWings: 
With its spacious interiors and upper deck, coupled with the cabins with en-suite bathrooms, its perfect venue for  
- Weekend getaways 
- Corporate events 
- Birthday Parties 
- Family Gathering 
- Product Launch 
- Networking Event 
- Wedding Ceremonies 
- Private Parties 
 
Boasting an incredible living space of 300 square metres, EagleWings is one of Singapore's largest catamarans -- a truly majestic location for any party or wedding.  
With its majestic exterior, the boat is even more impressive inside with sleek and modern furnishings such as spacious decks, a jacuzzi, fully-equipped bar, 10-seater dining space, and four luxurious cabins for overnight stays.  
 
Available for hourly, breakfast, lunch, dinner or full-day charters to short get-away (max 12 paxs). 
EagleWings can hold up to 50  guests onboard. 
Water toys (Sea Scooter, Sparks, Kayak, Banana Boat) are included. Ideal for family, friends and team-bonding.  
 
 
EagleWings II: 
New addition to Eaglewings Fleet, a powered cruiser from world-renowned Sunseeker Manhattan Series. 
With a maximum speed of 32 knots and 3000L fuel tank, this boat is deal for 
- Fishing Trips 
- Overseas getaways 
- Golf Trips 
- Small Private Parties 
- Island Explorations 
- Diving Trips 
 
 
** ​ 
We welcome you to visit us at One Degree 15 Marina
title: Eagelwings Yacht Charters Singapore
